total_subquestions_ys: Q1: Identify the unique numbers in the grid.

Q5: Determine the pattern of the numbers that are located on the right side of the vertical line.
Q6: Identify the number that is located at the top right corner of the grid.
Q7: Determine the pattern of the numbers that are located below the number identified in Q6.
Q8: Identify the number that is located at the bottom left corner of the grid.
Q9: Determine the pattern of the numbers that are located above the number identified in Q8.
Q10: Based on the patterns identified in Q2, Q4, Q5, Q7, and Q9, generate the output grid.
